text: Zagora–Mouresi (, ) is a municipality in the Magnesia regional unit, Thessaly, Greece. The seat of the municipality is the town Zagora.Kallikratis law Greece Ministry of Interior The municipality has an area of 150.315 km2. ==Municipality== The municipality Zagora–Mouresi was formed at the 2011 local government reform by the merger of the following 2 former municipalities, that became municipal units: *Mouresi *Zagora ==References== Category:Municipalities of Thessaly Category:Pelion
title: Zagora-Mouresi
